1. 查看当前zookeeper状态
```shell script
# 进入指定的zookeeper容器内部
docker exec -it [container name] bash
# 通过如下命令查看zookeeper
root@zoo3:/apache-zookeeper-3.5.6-bin# ./bin/zkServer.sh status
ZooKeeper JMX enabled by default
Using config: /conf/zoo.cfg
Client port found: 2181. Client address: localhost.
Mode: leader
```